  "description": {
   "en": "Manga adaptation of the \"10th place Next Light Novel Award 2023!(Paperback category)\" winner novel with the same name, written by Tsukasa author of \"Unlimited Fafnir\" illustrated by Shiratama.\n\nSota former vocalist of a popular band, having lost his former voice, he moves to a new high school where there is no one he knows to try to live quietly as Kanata Fujinami.\nHowever, when he meets Sora, an elementary school girl who wants to become a voice actor, Kanata's dormant heart is moved and the story of Sora's journey toward her dream begins.",
   "ja": "次にくるライトノベル大賞2023 10位入賞！（文庫部門）\n『銃皇無尽のファフニール』ツカサ氏と大人気イラストレーターしらたま氏初のライトノベルをコミカライズ！\n\n大人気バンドのボーカルをしていたソウタは、\n当時の声を失ったことで、誰も知らない転校先の高校で本名の藤波奏太（ふじなみかなた）としてひっそり暮らそうとしていた。\nだが、声優になりたい女子小学生・空（そら）と出会ったことで、奏太の心の変化と、空の夢へ向かう物語が始まる――。"
  },
